#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn1.32"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn1.32:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 1 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 1 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn1.32:0.2"
msgid "4. Satullapakāyikavagga "
msgstr "4. The Satullapa Group "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn1.32:0.3"
msgid "32. Maccharisutta "
msgstr "32. Stinginess "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn1.32:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn1.32:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho sambahulā satullapakāyikā devatāyo abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇā kevalakappaṃ jetavanaṃ obhāsetvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhaṃsu. "
msgstr "Then, late at night, several glorious deities of the Satullapa Group, lighting up the entire Jeta’s Grove, went up to the Buddha, bowed, and stood to one side. "

msgctxt "sn1.32:1.3"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho ekā devatā bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi: "
msgstr "Standing to one side, one deity recited this verse in the Buddha’s presence: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.40, sc2
msgctxt "sn1.32:2.1"
msgid "“Maccherā ca pamādā ca, "
msgstr "“Because of stinginess and negligence "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: dīyati → diyyati (mr)
msgctxt "sn1.32:2.2"
msgid "evaṃ dānaṃ na dīyati; "
msgstr "a gift is not given. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.32:2.3"
msgid "Puññaṃ ākaṅkhamānena, "
msgstr "Wanting merit, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.32:2.4"
msgid "deyyaṃ hoti vijānatā”ti. "
msgstr "a smart person would give.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn1.32:3.1"
msgid "Atha kho aparā devatā bhagavato santike imā gāthāyo abhāsi: "
msgstr "Then another deity recited these verses in the Buddha’s presence: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn1.32:4.1"
msgid "“Yasseva bhīto na dadāti maccharī, "
msgstr "“When a miser fails to give because of fear, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.32:4.2"
msgid "Tadevādadato bhayaṃ; "
msgstr "the very thing they’re afraid of comes to pass. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.32:4.3"
msgid "Jighacchā ca pipāsā ca, "
msgstr "The hunger and thirst "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.32:4.4"
msgid "Yassa bhāyati maccharī; "
msgstr "that a miser fears "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.32:4.5"
msgid "Tameva bālaṃ phusati, "
msgstr "hurt the fool "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.32:4.6"
msgid "Asmiṃ loke paramhi ca. "
msgstr "in this world and the next. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn1.32:5.1"
msgid "Tasmā vineyya maccheraṃ, "
msgstr "So you should dispel stinginess, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.32:5.2"
msgid "dajjā dānaṃ malābhibhū; "
msgstr "overcoming that stain, and give a gift. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.32:5.3"
msgid "Puññāni paralokasmiṃ, "
msgstr "The good deeds of sentient beings "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.32:5.4"
msgid "patiṭṭhā honti pāṇinan”ti. "
msgstr "support them in the next world.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn1.32:6.1"
msgid "Atha kho aparā devatā bhagavato santike imā gāthāyo abhāsi: "
msgstr "Then another deity recited these verses in the Buddha’s presence: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "sn1.32:7.1"
msgid "“Te matesu na mīyanti, "
msgstr "“Among the dead they do not die, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.32:7.2"
msgid "panthānaṃva sahabbajaṃ; "
msgstr "those who, like fellow travelers on the road, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.32:7.3"
msgid "Appasmiṃ ye pavecchanti, "
msgstr "are happy to provide, though they have but little. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.32:7.4"
msgid "esa dhammo sanantano. "
msgstr "This is an ancient principle. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.41, sc8
msgctxt "sn1.32:8.1"
msgid "Appasmeke pavecchanti, "
msgstr "Some who have little are happy to provide, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.32:8.2"
msgid "bahuneke na dicchare; "
msgstr "while some who have much don’t wish to give. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.32:8.3"
msgid "Appasmā dakkhiṇā dinnā, "
msgstr "An offering given from little "

# NOTE: Cf. Mark 12:41-44
#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.32:8.4"
msgid "sahassena samaṃ mitā”ti. "
msgstr "is multiplied a thousand times.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.19, sc9
msgctxt "sn1.32:9.1"
msgid "Atha kho aparā devatā bhagavato santike imā gāthāyo abhāsi: "
msgstr "Then another deity recited these verses in the Buddha’s presence: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc10
msgctxt "sn1.32:10.1"
msgid "“Duddadaṃ dadamānānaṃ, "
msgstr "“Giving what’s hard to give, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.32:10.2"
msgid "dukkaraṃ kamma kubbataṃ; "
msgstr "doing what’s hard to do; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.32:10.3"
msgid "Asanto nānukubbanti, "
msgstr "the wicked don’t act like this, "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: duranvayo → durannayo (bj, pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn1.32:10.4"
msgid "sataṃ dhammo duranvayo. "
msgstr "for the teaching of the good is hard to follow. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11
#. VAR: asataṃ → asatañca (bj, s1-3, km, pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn1.32:11.1"
msgid "Tasmā satañca asataṃ, "
msgstr "That’s why the virtuous and the wicked "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.32:11.2"
msgid "nānā hoti ito gati; "
msgstr "have different destinations after leaving this place. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.32:11.3"
msgid "Asanto nirayaṃ yanti, "
msgstr "The wicked go to hell, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.32:11.4"
msgid "santo saggaparāyanā”ti. "
msgstr "while the virtuous are bound for heaven.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc12
msgctxt "sn1.32:12.1"
msgid "Atha kho aparā devatā bhagavato santike etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then another deity said to the Buddha, "

msgctxt "sn1.32:12.2"
msgid "“kassa nu kho, bhagavā, subhāsitan”ti? "
msgstr "“Sir, who has spoken well?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc13
msgctxt "sn1.32:13.1"
msgid "“Sabbāsaṃ vo subhāsitaṃ pariyāyena; api ca mamapi suṇātha—"
msgstr "“You’ve all spoken well in your own way. However, listen to me also: "

# NOTE: reading samuñchaka
#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.42, sc14
msgctxt "sn1.32:14.1"
msgid "Dhammaṃ care yopi samuñjakaṃ care, "
msgstr "A hundred thousand people making a thousand sacrifices "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.32:14.2"
msgid "Dārañca posaṃ dadamappakasmiṃ; "
msgstr "isn’t worth a fraction "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.32:14.3"
msgid "Sataṃ sahassānaṃ sahassayāginaṃ, "
msgstr "of one who lives rightly, wandering for gleanings, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.32:14.4"
msgid "Kalampi nāgghanti tathāvidhassa te”ti. "
msgstr "or one who supports their partner from what little they have.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc15
msgctxt "sn1.32:15.1"
msgid "Atha kho aparā devatā bhagavantaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi: "
msgstr "Then another deity addressed the Buddha in verse: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc16
msgctxt "sn1.32:16.1"
msgid "“Kenesa yañño vipulo mahaggato, "
msgstr "“Why doesn’t that sacrifice of theirs, so abundant and magnificent, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.32:16.2"
msgid "Samena dinnassa na agghameti; "
msgstr "equal the value of a moral person’s gift? "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: Kathaṃ → idaṃ padaṃ si, pts1-2 potthakesu
msgctxt "sn1.32:16.3"
msgid "Kathaṃ sataṃ sahassānaṃ sahassayāginaṃ, "
msgstr "How is it that a hundred thousand people making a thousand sacrifices "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.32:16.4"
msgid "Kalampi nāgghanti tathāvidhassa te”ti. "
msgstr "isn’t worth a fraction of what’s offered by such a person?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc17
msgctxt "sn1.32:17.1"
msgid "“Dadanti heke visame niviṭṭhā, "
msgstr "“Some give based on immorality—"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.32:17.2"
msgid "Chetvā vadhitvā atha socayitvā; "
msgstr "after injuring, killing, and tormenting. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.32:17.3"
msgid "Sā dakkhiṇā assumukhā sadaṇḍā, "
msgstr "Such an offering—tearful, violent—"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.32:17.4"
msgid "Samena dinnassa na agghameti. "
msgstr "in no way equals the value of a moral person’s gift. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.43, sc18
msgctxt "sn1.32:18.1"
msgid "Evaṃ sataṃ sahassānaṃ sahassayāginaṃ, "
msgstr "That’s how it is that a hundred thousand people making a thousand sacrifices "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.32:18.2"
msgid "Kalampi nāgghanti tathāvidhassa te”ti. "
msgstr "isn’t worth a fraction of what’s offered by such a person.”"

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
